'''赛琳娜·金塔尼亚-佩雷斯'''（{{lang-es|Selena Quintanilla-Pérez}}，{{bd|1971年|4月16日|1995年|3月31日}}），通常简称'''赛琳娜'''（{{lang-en|Selena}}），是位美国创作歌手。她在《[[告示牌_(杂志)|告示牌]]》的[[公告牌热门拉丁单曲年终排行榜|热门拉丁单曲榜]]上有14首歌曲进入前十，其中7首还是[[冠军|冠军]]曲目，《告示牌》因此称她为“90年代顶级拉丁艺人”（{{lang|en|top Latin artist of the '90s}}）和“十年最畅销拉丁艺人”（{{lang|en|Best selling Latin artist of the decade}}）<ref name="selena">{{cite journal | last = Mayfield | first = Geoff | date = 1999-12-25 | title = Totally '90s: Diary of a Decade | journal = Billboard | publisher = Nielsen Business Media, Inc. | volume = 111 | issue = 52 | issn = 0006-2510 | accessdate = 2014-07-18 | page = YE–16–18 | url = http://books.google.com.mx/books?id=9w0EAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA66&dq=selena | archive-date = 2011-07-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110722223825/http://books.google.com.mx/books?id=9w0EAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA66&dq=selena | dead-url = no }}</ref>。1994到1995年最成功的两首拉丁单曲{{lang|en|《[[Amor_Prohibido_(歌曲)|Amor Prohibido]]》}}和《{{lang|en|[[No_Me_Queda_Más|No Me Queda Más]]}}》都是赛琳娜的作品<ref name="billboardmag">{{cite journal | last = | first = | date = 1998-11-28 | title = Topping The Charts Year By Year | journal = Billboard | publisher = Nielsen Business Media, Inc. | volume = 110 | issue = 48 | page = LMQ3 | url = http://books.google.com/?id=MAoEAAAAMBAJ&pg=RA1-PA38&dq=rudy+la+scala&cd=1#v=onepage&q=rudy%20la%20scala | accessdate = 2014-07-18}}</ref>，她还被称为“[[流行音乐领域的尊称#S|特加諾音樂女王]]”<ref name="Mitchell-1995">{{cite news | first = Rick | last = Mitchell | archivedate = 2007-08-10 | url = http://www.chron.com/content/chronicle/metropolitan/selena/95/05/21/legend.html | title = Selena | work = Houston Chronicle | deadurl = yes | date = 1995-05-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070810050339/http://www.chron.com/content/chronicle/metropolitan/selena/95/05/21/legend.html}}</ref>和墨西哥的[[麦当娜|麦当娜]]<ref name="Verhovek">{{cite news | author = Sam Howe Verhovek | title = Grammy Winning Singer Selena Killed in Shooting at Texas Motel | page = 1 | work = The New York Times | date = 1995-04-01 | url = http://www.nytimes.com/1995/04/01/obituaries/grammy-winning-singer-selena-killed-in-shooting-at-texas-motel.html | deadurl = no | publisher = The New York Times Company | archivedate = 2013-12-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131220142034/http://www.nytimes.com/1995/04/01/obituaries/grammy-winning-singer-selena-killed-in-shooting-at-texas-motel.html}}</ref>。赛琳娜在自己12岁时就发行了第一张专辑《{{lang|en|Selena y Los Dinos}}》。1987年，她赢得了特哈诺音乐奖的年度最佳女歌手奖，并在几年后与{{lang|en|[[EMI|EMI]]}}签订唱片合约。20世纪90年代早期，她的知名度与日俱增（特别是在[[西班牙语|西班牙语]]国家），并且也开始录制英语歌曲。

1995年3月31日，赛琳娜遭自己前任粉丝俱乐部主席[[约兰达·萨尔迪瓦|约兰达·萨尔迪瓦]]（{{lang|en|Yolanda Saldívar}}）谋杀，终年23岁。两星期后的1995年4月12日，[[德克萨斯州州长名单|德克萨斯州州长]][[乔治·沃克·布什|乔治·沃克·布什]]宣布赛琳娜的生日（4月16日）成为该州的“赛琳娜节”<ref name="rolemodel">{{cite web | last = Orozco | first = Cynthia E. | url = http://www.tshaonline.org/handbook/online/articles/fquxg | title = Quintanilla Pérez, Selena | work = The Handbook of Texas online | accessdate = 2009-04-26 | publisher = Texas State Historical Association | archive-date = 2020-04-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200407230025/https://tshaonline.org/handbook/online/articles/fquxg | dead-url = no }}</ref>。1997年，[[华纳兄弟|华纳兄弟]]以她生平改编的电影《[[哭泣的玫瑰|哭泣的玫瑰]]》上映，[[詹妮弗·洛佩兹|詹妮弗·洛佩兹]]在其中饰演赛琳娜。[[音乐剧|音乐]][[舞台剧|舞台剧]]《[[永远的赛琳娜|永远的赛琳娜]]》也是以她的生平改编，[[维罗尼卡_(歌手)|维罗尼卡·巴斯克斯]]（{{lang|en|Veronica Vazquez}}）扮演赛琳娜。2006年6月，[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]][[科珀斯克里斯蒂_(得克萨斯州)|科珀斯克里斯蒂]]树立起一座真人大小的赛琳娜铜像，还开设了一家赛琳娜博物馆。截至2014年3月，她的唱片在全世界共计售出了超过6000万张<ref name="Selena sales">{{cite web | title = Still Missing Selena: Here Are 6 Reasons Why | work = NBC News | accessdate = 2014-07-18 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140701155612/http://www.nbcnews.com/news/latino/still-missing-selena-here-are-6-reasons-why-n66031 | url = http://www.nbcnews.com/news/latino/still-missing-selena-here-are-6-reasons-why-n66031 | archivedate = 2014-07-01}}</ref>，是历史上作品最畅销的艺人之一。截至2014年6月，她仍是历史上作品销售排行第3的拉丁艺人，仅次于[[格洛丽亚·埃斯特凡|格洛丽亚·埃斯特凡]]（冠军）和[[夏奇拉|夏奇拉]]（[[亚军|亚军]]）<ref name="Selena News Report">{{cite web | title = Selena Just Behind Gloria Estefan and Shakira | url = http://m.youtube.com/watch?v=lqslhWfDt50 | work = Televisa | accessdate = 2014-03-31}}</ref>。她还是仅有的一位在[[公告牌二百强专辑榜|公告牌二百强专辑榜]]上同时有5张专辑上榜的女艺人<ref name="sales">{{cite web | title = A 17 años de su trágica muerte, Selena Quintanilla vuelve en grande. | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131007215321/http://la.eonline.com/venezuela/2012/audio-a-17-an-os-de-su-tragica-muerte-selena-quintanilla-vuelve-en-grande | archivedate = 2013-10-07 | deadurl = no | work = E! Online | accessdate = 2014-07-18 | url = http://la.eonline.com/venezuela/2012/audio-a-17-an-os-de-su-tragica-muerte-selena-quintanilla-vuelve-en-grande}}</ref>。[[纽约州|纽约州]][[奥尔巴尼|奥尔巴尼]]的《[[联合时报_(奥尔巴尼)|联合时报]]》（{{lang|en|''Times Union''}}）把赛琳娜评为“历史上100位最酷的美国人”之一<ref name="americanhistory">{{cite news | title = The 100 coolest Americans in history | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140227172943/http://www.timesunion.com/entertainment/article/The-100-coolest-Americans-in-history-5252418.php#photo-5914364 | archivedate = 2014-02-27 | deadurl = no | newspaper = Times Union | url = http://www.timesunion.com/entertainment/article/The-100-coolest-Americans-in-history-5252418.php#photo-5914364 | accessdate = 2014-07-18 | date = 2014-02-20}}</ref>。

== 早年生活 ==
赛琳娜于1971年4月16日在美国[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]][[布拉佐里亚县|布拉佐里亚县]]的莱克杰克逊<ref name="Patoski">{{cite book | ref = harv | last = Patoski | first = Joe Nick | title = Selena: Como La Flor | year = 1996 | publisher = Little Brown and Company | location = Boston | isbn = 0-316-69378-2}}</ref>{{rp|30}}出生，是家里三个孩子的老幺<ref name="BaylorHSA">{{cite web | url = http://www.baylor.edu/mediacommunications/news.php?action=story&story=3687 | title = HSA Banquet Features Father of Late Tejano Star Selena | work = Baylor University press release | publisher = Baylor® University | date = 1999-11-04 | accessdate = 2014-07-18 | archivedate = 2014-07-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140704072548/http://www.baylor.edu/mediacommunications/news.php?action=story&story=3687}}</ref>。她的父亲[[小亚伯拉罕·金塔尼利亚|小亚伯拉罕·金塔尼利亚]]（{{lang|en|Abraham Quintanilla, Jr.}}）是墨西哥裔美国人，母亲马塞拉·奥菲利亚（{{lang|en|Marcella Ofelia}}）的[[女性人名|娘家姓]]是萨莫拉（{{lang|en|Samora}}），拥有一半[[切罗基人|切罗基美洲原住民]]和一半[[墨西哥裔美国人|墨西哥裔美国人]]血统<ref name="Patoski" />{{rp|22}}<ref>{{cite book | last = Ware | first = Susan | title = Notable American Women: A Biographical Dictionary | url = https://archive.org/details/notableamericanw0000unse | publisher = Harvard University Press | year = 2005 | isbn = 0-674-01488-X}}</ref>。赛琳娜在[[耶和华见证人|耶和华见证人]]教堂的环境下长大<ref name="Caller-Times-1997">{{cite web | author = Caller-Times | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140718041415/http://www.caller.com/entertainment/selena/birthday-hoopla-prohibited | url = http://www.caller.com/entertainment/selena/birthday-hoopla-prohibited | title = Birthday hoopla is prohibited | publisher = Caller.com | date = 1997-04-16 | location = Corpus Christi, Texas | archivedate = 2014-07-18 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-07-18}}</ref>。她3岁就开始学习唱歌，到了9岁那年，父亲把自己的三个孩子一起组建成一个声乐演唱组合，起名叫“{{lang|en|Selena y Los Dinos}}”（字面意为“赛琳娜和弟兄们”）<ref name="Verhovek" />。几个孩子先是在家里开办的餐馆表演<ref name="rolemodel" />，但餐馆之后不久就因生意不佳倒闭。接下来一家人搬到了[[科珀斯克里斯蒂_(德克萨斯州)|科珀斯克里斯蒂]]，演唱组合会利用任何能够得到的机会表演，例如街头巷尾、婚礼、成年礼和市集等<ref name="Patoski" />{{rp|53}}。随着赛琳娜的受欢迎程度与日俱增，她的演出和旅行安排开始妨碍到教育，父亲在她读8年级时就让她退了学<ref name="Mitchell-1995" />。17岁那年，赛琳娜通过美国学校课程取得了高中文凭<ref name="Patoski" />{{rp|59}}。

乐队的努力获得了回报，1985年，年仅14岁的赛琳娜为一家唱片公司录制了第一张专辑。她的父亲买下了所有的原版拷贝<ref name="Patoski" />{{rp|49}}，之后在1995年以《我的第一张唱片》（{{lang|es|''Mis Primeras Grabaciones''}}）之名发行<ref name="Patoski" />{{rp|288}}。之后的3年时间里，她还发行了另外6张专辑，但并没有签订合约。

== 事业成功 ==
赛琳娜获得了1987年特哈诺音乐奖的年度最佳女歌手奖，并且余生中每一年都将赢得这座奖项<ref name="Mitchell-1995" /><ref name="TejanoAward">{{cite web | work = CBSNews.com | date = 2002-10-17 | accessdate = 2014-07-18 | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/news/fans-family-remember-selena/  | title = Fans, Family Remember Selena | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131212234410/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/fans-family-remember-selena/ | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-12-12}}</ref>。1989年，前[[索尼音乐娱乐|索尼拉丁音乐]]总裁何塞·贝哈尔（{{lang|es|José Behar}}）与赛琳娜签订了{{lang|en|[[Capitol唱片|Capitol]]/[[EMI|EMI]]}}的合同，他之后表示自己发现了又一位[[格洛丽亚·埃斯特凡|格洛丽亚·埃斯特凡]]<ref name="Mitchell-1995" />。1988年，赛琳娜结识了自己拥有乐队的歌手克里斯·佩雷斯。两年后，金塔尼利亚一家聘请佩雷斯加入赛琳娜的乐队，两人还开始了交往。她的父亲起初反对两人交往，甚至还开除了佩雷斯，但最后还是接受了两人的关系<ref name="Patoski" />。1992年4月2日，赛琳娜和佩雷斯在德克萨斯州的[[努埃塞斯县_(得克萨斯州)|努埃塞斯县]]登记结婚<ref name="Verhovek" />。

1990年，她的专辑《{{lang|es|Ven Conmigo}}》（字面意为《跟我来》）发行，其中的歌曲由兄长兼乐队歌曲主创亚伯拉罕·金塔尼利亚三世创作，成为历史上第一张由女艺人录制并达到金唱片销量的特哈诺专辑。同期，赛琳娜的粉丝、注册护士约兰达·萨尔迪瓦找到赛琳娜的父亲，提议组建粉丝俱乐部。小亚伯拉罕同意了这个建议，并让萨尔迪瓦担任俱乐部主席和赛琳娜一家零售商店的经理<ref name="Verhovek" />。1992年，赛琳娜的新唱片《{{lang|es|[[Entre_a_Mi_Mundo|Entre a Mi Mundo]]}}》（意为《走进我的世界》）获得成功，其中的歌曲《{{lang|en|Como La Flor}}》（意为《像花一样》）对她的事业起到了很大的推动作用。下一张专辑《{{lang|en|[[Selena_Live!|Selena Live!]]}}》（意为《赛琳娜现场》）则在[[第36届格莱美奖|第36届]][[格莱美奖|格莱美奖]]角逐中赢得了[[格莱美奖最佳最佳墨西哥/墨西哥-美国专辑|墨西哥-美国专辑奖]]<ref name="Verhovek" />。
{{Listen|filename=Selena-ComoLaFlor.ogg|title=Como La Flor|description=《{{lang|en|Como La Flor}}》是赛琳娜最知名的西班牙语歌曲之一。|format=[[Ogg|Ogg]]}}

1994年，赛琳娜发行了专辑《{{lang|es|Amor Prohibido}}》，这张唱片获得了格莱美奖年度最佳墨西哥-美国专辑提名。这年她和乐队还获得了更多的荣誉。《[[告示牌_(杂志)|告示牌]]》杂志的“我们的事情奖”（{{lang|es|Premio Lo Nuestro}}）授予他们6座奖项，包括最佳拉丁艺人和《{{lang|es|Como La Flor}}》获得的年度最佳歌曲奖。同时，她与{{lang|en|[[Barrio_Boyzz|Barrio Boyzz]]}}（字面意为“巴里奥男孩”）合作的歌曲《{{lang|es|[[Donde_Quiera_Que_Estés|Donde Quiera Que Estés]]}}》（意为《无论你在哪》）在[[热门拉丁歌曲|告示牌拉丁歌曲榜]]上冲至冠军位置，赛琳娜因此决定在拉美进行巡演<ref name="Patoski" />{{rp|123}}。她与[[萨尔瓦多|萨尔瓦多]]歌手阿尔瓦罗·托雷斯（{{lang|es|álvaro Torres}}）对唱了歌曲《{{lang|es|[[Buenos_Amigos|Buenos Amigos]]}}》（意为《好朋友》）。到1994年秋，《{{lang|es|Amor Prohibido}}》已经在墨西哥获得了商业上的成功，其中有4首歌曲登上拉丁歌曲榜首，在排行榜上取代格洛丽亚·埃斯特凡的《{{lang|es|[[Mi_Tierra|Mi Tierra]]}}》（意为《我的故土》）成为新的冠军专辑。到1994年末，唱片已在美国售出40万张，墨西哥5万张，达到金唱片标准<ref name="Verhovek" />。

除了音乐外，赛琳娜也在1994年开始设计和制作服装，在科珀斯克里斯蒂和[[圣安东尼奥_(得克萨斯州)|圣安东尼奥]]各开办了一家服装店，其中都配备有美容院<ref name="Patoski" />{{rp|120}}。《西班牙商业》（{{lang|en|''Hispanic Business''}}）[[杂志|杂志]]报道称，赛琳娜在这两家服装店的收益超过500万美元<ref name="Fivemillion">{{cite news|url=http://www.caller.com/ccct/home/article/0,1641,CCCT_800_3654650,00.html |title=Selena – Life Events |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070312061532/http://www.caller.com/ccct/home/article/0%2C1641%2CCCCT_800_3654650%2C00.html |publisher=Corpus Christi Caller Times |date=2005-03-27 |accessdate=2007-03-12 |archivedate=2007-03-12 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。赛琳娜还曾短暂地在墨西哥[[肥皂剧|肥皂剧]]《[[两个女人一条路|两个女人一条路]]》（{{lang|es|''Dos Mujeres, Un Camino''}}）中和[[埃里克·埃斯特拉达|埃里克·埃斯特拉达]]（{{lang|en|Erik Estrada}}）演对手戏<ref name="Patoski" />{{rp|134}}。1995年，她还开始协商出演埃米利奥·拉罗萨（{{lang|en|Emilio Larrosa}}）制作的另一部肥皂剧<ref name="Patoski" />{{rp|134}}。

达到事业高峰的同时，赛琳娜以家庭为中心，积极参与禁毒和提高[[艾滋病|艾滋病]]意识的宣传活动。从1995年开始，她计划要在美国流行音乐主流领域取得突破，并于这年春开始制作自己的第一张英语专辑。<ref name="allmusic">{{cite web | url = http://www.allmusic.com/artist/selena-mn0000004852/biography | title = Selena | author = Sandra Brennan | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131128213310/http://www.allmusic.com/artist/selena-mn0000004852/biography | deadurl = no | work = AllMusic.com | publisher = All Media Network, LLC. | accessdate = 2014-07-18 | archivedate = 2013-11-28}}</ref>

== 谋杀 ==
1995年初，金塔尼利亚一家发现约兰达·萨尔迪瓦一直在[[侵吞|挪用]]粉丝俱乐部的资金，决定解除她的职务<ref name="Verhovek" />。三个星期后，赛琳娜同意在科珀斯克里斯蒂一家[[戴斯酒店|戴斯]]汽车旅馆和萨尔迪瓦见面<ref name="DaysInn">{{cite web | title = October 13, 1995, testimony of Richard Fredrickson | archivedate = 2007-04-05 | deadurl = yes | date = 1995-10-13 | publisher = Houston Chronicle | accessdate = 2007-04-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070405104003/http://chron.com/content/chronicle/metropolitan/selena/transcripts/95/10/13/param.html | url = http://chron.com/content/chronicle/metropolitan/selena/transcripts/95/10/13/param.html}}</ref>，希望拿到萨尔迪瓦之前一直拒绝交出的财务记录。萨尔迪瓦又一次推迟了移交，声称自己在墨西哥遭到了[[强奸|强奸]]<ref name="Mitchell-1995" />。赛琳娜于是开车把对方送到当地一家医院，但大夫没有发现任何[[证据|证据]]表明当事人有受过强奸<ref name="Rape">{{cite web | url = http://chron.com/content/chronicle/metropolitan/selena/transcripts/95/10/12/anthony.html | date = 1995-10-12 | title = October 12, 1995 testimony of Carla Anthony | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2007-08-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070807104313/http://chron.com/content/chronicle/metropolitan/selena/transcripts/95/10/12/anthony.html | accessdate = 2007-08-07 | publisher = Houston Chronicle}}</ref>。两人回到汽车旅馆，赛琳娜再次要求对方交出财务记录<ref name="Verhovek" />，对此萨尔迪瓦的反应是从皮包里掏出手枪指向赛琳娜。赛琳娜试着逃跑，但对方从背后开枪打中她的右肩，切断了一条[[动脉|动脉]]。已受致命重伤的赛琳娜跑向大厅求助，她因体力不支倒在地上，店员马上打了911报警电话，萨尔迪瓦仍在后面追赶，一边嘴里咒骂她是个“婊子”<ref name="Bitch">{{cite web | date = 1995-10-12 | url = http://www.chron.com/content/chronicle/metropolitan/selena/transcripts/95/10/12/martinez.html | title = October 12, 1995, the testimony of Norma Martinez | publisher = Houston Chronicle | accessdate = 2007-08-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070810090748/http://www.chron.com/content/chronicle/metropolitan/selena/transcripts/95/10/12/martinez.html | archivedate = 2007-08-10 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。1995年3月31日下午13点05分，赛琳娜因[[出血|失血过多]]在医院辞世，这时距她的24岁生日还差16天<ref name="Death">{{cite web | last1 = Villafranca | first1 = Armando | last2 = Reinert | first2 = Patty | date = 1995-04-01 | archivedate = 2007-08-22 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070822022317/http://www.chron.com/content/chronicle/metropolitan/selena/95/04/01/killed.html | url = http://www.chron.com/content/chronicle/metropolitan/selena/95/04/01/killed.html | title = Singer Selena shot to death | publisher = Houston Chronicle | accessdate = 2007-08-22}}</ref>。她的遗体下葬在科珀斯克里斯蒂的海滨纪念公园<ref>{{cite book | last = Harvey | first = Bill | title = Texas Cemeteries: The Resting Places of Famous, Infamous, and Just Plain Interesting Texans | url = https://archive.org/details/texascemeteriesr00harv | year = 2003 | publisher = University of Texas Press | isbn = 0-292-73466-2 | page = [https://archive.org/details/texascemeteriesr00harv/page/92 92]}}</ref>。

=== 影响 ===
赛琳娜遭到谋杀一事产生了广泛的影响。美国各大电视台都中断了日常节目插播这条新闻，[[汤姆·布罗考|汤姆·布罗考]]（{{lang|en|Tom Brokaw}}）在节目中称赛琳娜是“墨西哥的[[麦当娜|麦当娜]]”<ref name="Maddona">{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100803024420/http://www.pacificnews.org/jinn/stories/3.06/970321-selena.html | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.pacificnews.org/jinn/stories/3.06/970321-selena.html | title = Selena's Story -- "Pochos" Have Come of Age | author = Gregory Rodriguez | publisher = Pacific News | date = 1997-03-21 | accessdate = 2010-08-03 | archivedate = 2010-08-03}}</ref>。《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》在她去世两天后以头版详述这一新闻<ref name="Patoski" />{{rp|174}}。多地为她举行了守夜和纪念活动，德克萨斯州的多家电台不间断地播放她的音乐<ref name="queen">{{cite web | last = Mitchell | first = Rick | date = 1995-05-21 | url = http://www.chron.com/content/chronicle/metropolitan/selena/95/05/21/legend.html | title = Selena | publisher = Houston Chronicle | accessdate = 2007-08-10 | archivedate = 2007-08-10 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070810050339/http://www.chron.com/content/chronicle/metropolitan/selena/95/05/21/legend.html}}</ref>。有6万人前来送葬，其中许多人还是专程从别的国家赶来<ref name="queen" />。包括[[格洛丽亚·埃斯特凡|格洛丽亚·埃斯特凡]]、[[西莉亚·克鲁兹|西莉亚·克鲁兹]]（{{lang|en|Celia Cruz}}）、[[胡利奥·伊格莱西亚斯|胡利奥·伊格莱西亚斯]]和麦当娜在内的多位名流致电赛琳娜的家人表示哀悼<ref name="Patoski" />{{rp|165}}。《[[人物_(杂志)|人物]]》出版了一期纪念特刊《赛琳娜（1971至1995），她的图片人生》（{{lang|en|''Selena 1971–1995, Her Life in Pictures''}}），纪念她的生平和音乐事业<ref name="queen" />，卖出了近45万份。两个星期后，该公司又为赛琳娜出版了一期特刊，卖出了超过60万份<ref name="Latin pride">{{cite journal | last = Lannert | first = John | year = 1995 | title = Latin pride | journal = Billboard | volume = 107 | issue = 23 | page = 112 | accessdate = 2014-07-18 | url = http://books.google.com/?id=0QsEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA62&dq=Selena+Dreaming+of+You+sold+more#v=onepage&q=Selena%20Dreaming%20of%20You%20sold%20more&f=false}}</ref>。几天后，[[霍华德·斯特恩|霍华德·斯特恩]]（{{lang|en|Howard Stern}}）嘲笑了赛琳娜被谋杀一案和之后的葬礼，还取笑了她的送葬者，批评她的音乐，称“这音乐对我一点意义也没有，哪怕就是[[艾尔文与花栗鼠|艾尔文与花栗鼠]]（{{lang|en|Alvin and the Chipmunks}}）也更有灵魂……说西班牙语的人在音乐上的品味实在糟掉底儿了。他们一点深度都没有。”德克萨斯州的西班牙语族裔群体对斯特恩的评论感到出离愤怒<ref name="Stern">{{cite web | last1 = Asin | first1 = Stephanie | last2 = Dyer | first2 = R.A. | url = http://www.chron.com/content/chronicle/metropolitan/selena/95/04/06/stern.html | title = Selena's public outraged: Shock jock Howard Stern's comments hit raw nerve | publisher = Houston Chronicle | date = 1995-04-06 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070810122944/http://www.chron.com/content/chronicle/metropolitan/selena/95/04/06/stern.html | accessdate = 2007-08-10 | archivedate = 2007-08-10 }}</ref>。甚至有[[法院|法院]]向他发出了[[行为不检|行为不检]]的逮捕令，对此斯特恩在节目中以西班牙语发布道歉声明，强调自己的评论无意对“她的家人、朋友和所有爱她的人（造成）更多痛苦”<ref name="NYDailyNews1995">{{cite web | title = A real shocker from Stern: Apology for Selena comments | work = New York Daily News | accessdate = 2014-07-18 | date = 1995-04-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131203070256/http://www.nydailynews.com/archives/entertainment/real-shocker-stern-apology-selena-comments-article-1.689006 | archivedate = 2013-12-03 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nydailynews.com/archives/entertainment/real-shocker-stern-apology-selena-comments-article-1.689006}}</ref><ref name="ABCNews2012">{{cite web | last = Marikar | first = Sheila | title = Howard Stern's Five Most Outrageous Offenses | url = http://abcnews.go.com/Entertainment/howard-sterns-outrageous-offenses/story?id=16327309 | publisher = ABC Good Morning America | accessdate = 2014-07-18 | date = 2012-05-14 | archivedate = 2014-07-15 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140715175129/http://abcnews.go.com/Entertainment/howard-sterns-outrageous-offenses/story?id=16327309}}</ref>。1995年4月12日，当时的德克萨斯州[[州长|州长]][[乔治·沃克·布什|乔治·沃克·布什]]宣布赛琳娜的生日（4月16日）为该州的“赛琳娜节”<ref name="rolemodel" />。这年赛琳娜还得以入选“拉丁音乐名人堂”<ref name="Latin pride" />。

1995年夏，赛琳娜混合西班牙语歌曲和新录制英语曲目的专辑《{{lang|en|[[Dreaming_of_You|Dreaming of You]]}}》（意为《梦见你》）一经推出就登上了美国[[公告牌二百强专辑榜|公告牌二百强专辑榜]]冠军位置，这在历史上的所有西班牙语歌手中还是头一遭<ref name="firstHispanicsinger">{{cite web | last = Hodges | first= Ann | archivedate = 2009-02-04 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090204134420/http://www.chron.com/content/chronicle/features/96/12/07/selena.0-0.html | url = http://www.chron.com/content/chronicle/features/96/12/07/selena.0-0.html | title = Selena legend lives on with TV movie | publisher = Houston Chronicle | date = 1996-12-06 | accessdate = 2009-02-04}}</ref>，并且销量即使是在所有歌手中也能排到第2位，仅次于[[迈克尔·杰克逊|迈克尔·杰克逊]]的《{{lang|en|[[HIStory:_Past,_Present_and_Future,_Book_I|HIStory]]}}》。《{{lang|en|Dreaming of You}}》发行当天就卖出了17.5万张，创下女性流行歌手的新纪录，第一年则共计卖出了200万份<ref name="Copies">{{cite web | url = http://chron.com/content/chronicle/metropolitan/selena/96/03/31d.html | archivedate = 2007-04-06 | title = In the spirit of Selena: Tributes, a book and an impending film testify to the Tejano singer's enduring | publisher = Houston Chronicle | date = 1996-03-31 | accessdate = 2007-04-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070406190828/http://chron.com/content/chronicle/metropolitan/selena/96/03/31d.html | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。《{{lang|en|Dreaming of You}}》发行第一周共售出超过33万份拷贝<ref name="Patoski" />{{rp|199}}<ref>{{cite journal | author = Nilou Panahpour | year = 1995 | title = Rock and Roll yearbook, the best in music, movies, and television | journal = Rolling Stone | publisher = Straight Arrow Publishers Company | volume = | issue = 724/725 | page = 64}}</ref>，还在[[贝塔斯曼音乐集团|贝塔斯曼音乐集团]]美国最畅销唱片排行榜上名列第75位<ref>{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131025112551/http://www.mi2n.com/press.php3?press_nb=47877 |archivedate=2013-10-25 |url=http://www.mi2n.com/press.php3?press_nb=47877 |title=List of BMG Music Club's top selling albums in the United States |publisher=BMG |accessdate=2014-07-18 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。包括《{{lang|en|[[I_Could_Fall_in_Love|I Could Fall in Love]]}}》（意为《我可以陷入情网》）和《{{lang|en|[[Dreaming_of_You_(歌曲)|Dreaming of You]]}}》（意为《梦见你》）在内的多首歌曲得以在许多主流英语广播电台播放，其中《{{lang|en|Dreaming of You}}》在[[告示牌百强单曲榜|告示牌百强单曲榜]]排到了第21位。同时《{{lang|en|I Could Fall in Love}}》虽然当时不符合百强单曲榜的上榜资格，但还是在电台百首热门单曲榜上排到了第8位，并且打入成人现代歌曲榜的前十。《{{lang|en|Dreaming of You}}》先后35次得到[[美国唱片业协会|美国唱片业协会]]拉丁音乐领域的[[音乐唱片销售认证|白金认证]]<ref>{{cite web | title = RIAA – Gold & Platinum | accessdate = 2009-01-04 | work = RIAA | url = http://riaa.com/goldandplatinumdata.php?resultpage=1&table=SEARCH_RESULTS&action=&title=dreaming%20of%20you&startYear=1958&endYear=2009&sort=Artist&perPage=25 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151105220152/http://riaa.com/goldandplatinumdata.php?resultpage=1&table=SEARCH_RESULTS&action=&title=dreaming%20of%20you&startYear=1958&endYear=2009&sort=Artist&perPage=25 | archivedate = 2015-11-05 }}</ref>，亦為香港電視劇《[[壹號皇庭|壹號皇庭]]IV》的插曲之一。1995年10月，[[休斯敦|休斯敦]]的一个[[陪审团|陪审团]]判决萨尔迪瓦[[谋杀|谋杀]]罪名成立并处以[[无期徒刑|终身监禁]]，至少要30年后才有可能获得[[假释|假释]]<ref name="convicted">{{cite news | last = Graczyk | first = Michael | title = Selena's killer gets life | agency = Associated Press | archivedate = 2007-04-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070405221519/http://chron.com/content/chronicle/metropolitan/95/10/26/sentence.html | url = http://chron.com/content/chronicle/metropolitan/95/10/26/sentence.html | date = 1995-10-26 | accessdate = 2007-04-05 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。根据[[法官|法官]]的命令，杀害赛琳娜的枪于2002年销毁，残渣抛入了[[科珀斯克里斯蒂湾|科珀斯克里斯蒂湾]]<ref name="Gun">{{cite web | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2002/06/08/us/national-briefing-southwest-texas-gun-that-killed-singer-is-to-be-destroyed.html | title = National Briefing Southwest: Texas: Gun That Killed Singer Is To Be Destroyed | work = The New York Times | date = 2008-06-08 | publisher = The New York Times Company | accessdate = 2014-07-18 | archivedate = 2013-06-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130602151508/http://www.nytimes.com/2002/06/08/us/national-briefing-southwest-texas-gun-that-killed-singer-is-to-be-destroyed.html | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | archivedate = 2013-10-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131004213707/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2002-06-11/news/0206110189_1_tejano-singing-star-selena-abraham-quintanilla-corpus-christi-bay | title = Gun used in slaying of Selena destroyed | deadurl = no | url = http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2002-06-11/news/0206110189_1_tejano-singing-star-selena-abraham-quintanilla-corpus-christi-bay | publisher = Chicago Tribune | work = chicagotribune.com | accessdate = 2014-07-18 | date = 2002-06-11 | first = Items | last = Compiled}}</ref>。

== 追思、知名度及榮譽 ==
[[File:Selena_memorial.jpg|upright]]

1997年，[[华纳兄弟|华纳兄弟]]根据赛琳娜生平改编的电影《[[哭泣的玫瑰|哭泣的玫瑰]]》上映，[[詹妮弗·洛佩兹|詹妮弗·洛佩兹]]在片中饰演赛琳娜<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1073427-selena/ | title = Selena (1997) | work = Rotten Tomatoes | publisher = Flixster | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131215205055/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1073427-selena/ | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-12-15}}</ref>；[[音乐剧|音乐]][[舞台剧|舞台剧]]《永远的赛琳娜》也是以她的生平改编，维罗尼卡·巴斯克斯扮演赛琳娜<ref>{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120205000905/http://www.edgallardo.com/selena.htm | title = I Can't Stop Dreaming of You ... | accessdate = 2012-02-05 | url = http://www.edgallardo.com/selena.htm | archivedate = 2012-02-05 | deadurl = yes | work = edgallardo.com}}</ref>。赛琳娜还于2001年成为唱片销量最高的三位拉丁艺人之一<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Oumano | first1 = Elena | year = 1999 | title = U.S. Latin Music Sales Break Records | journal = Billboard magazine | volume = 111 | issue = 43 | page = 108 | accessdate = 2014-07-18 | url = http://books.google.com/?id=dwgEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA96&dq=Selena+breaks+records#v=onepage&q&f=false}}</ref>。2011年3月16日，[[美国邮政署|美国邮政署]]发行了“拉丁传奇”纪念邮票，纪念包括赛琳娜、[[卡洛斯·葛戴尔|卡洛斯·葛戴尔]]、西莉亚·克鲁兹、[[铁托·普恩特|铁托·普恩特]]（{{lang|en|Tito Puente}}）和[[卡门·米兰达|卡门·米兰达]]（{{lang|en|Carmen Miranda}}）在内的多位拉丁艺人<ref name="stamps">{{cite web | publisher = NewsTaco | accessdate = 2014-07-18 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130515142716/http://www.newstaco.com/2011/01/18/selena-celia-cruz-tito-puente-in-u-s-postal-stamp-form/ | url = http://www.newstaco.com/2011/01/18/selena-celia-cruz-tito-puente-in-u-s-postal-stamp-form/ | title = Selena, Celia Cruz, Tito Puente In U.S. Postal Stamp Form | author = Sara Inés Calderón | date = 2011-01-18 | archivedate = 2013-05-15}}</ref>。截至2014年3月，赛琳娜的唱片在全世界的销量已经超过6000万张<ref name="Selena sales" />。
2017年11月3日，赛琳娜成為好萊塢星光大道第2,622顆星星，紀念她在音樂上的貢獻，星星地點在國會唱片大樓前方(1750 N. Vine Street)。<ref>[http://time.com/5010432/where-is-selena-quintanilla-star-in-hollywood/ Selena Honored With Star on the Hollywood Walk of Fame]</ref>

